\label{thm:main}
Let $\F$ be a $(1-\eps)$-approximate union closed set system, where $\eps < 1/2$. Then there is an element which is contained in a $\psi-\delta$ fraction of sets in $\F$, where $\delta=2 \eps \left( 1 + \frac{\log(1/\eps)}{\log |\F|} \right)$.
